      "created_at": "2018-02-25T02:02:15.610Z",
      "cooked": "<p>120 bpm, u pa sepse vendi 19 i listes 2017…<br>\nMerr pak kohe “120 bpm” per t’i dhene aprovim. thx.</p>",
